[][627] +    // Method Description:
[][628] +    // - Connects event handlers to the TermControl for events that we want to
[][629] +    //   handle. This includes:
[][630] +    //    * the Copy and Paste events, for setting and retrieving clipboard data
[][631] +    //      on the right thread
[][632] +    //    * the TitleChanged event, for changing the text of the tab
[][633] +    //    * the GotFocus event, for changing the title/icon in the tab when a new
[][634] +    //      control is focused
[][635] +    // Arguments:
[][636] +    // - term: The newly created TermControl to connect the events for
[][637] +    // - hostingTab: The Tab that's hosting this TermControl instance
